<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Best Scrabble Words With K — Strategy & High Scorers</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">K is Scrabble's quiet powerhouse — 5 points with only 1 tile in the bag. Unlike flashier tiles like Q or Z, K combines easily with common letters (CK, KE, KI, NK) and creates short, punchy words perfect for tight boards. A well-placed K on a double-letter square delivers 10 points from a single tile.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">K Tile at a Glance</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">5 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Tile value</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">1</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Tile in bag</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">CK NK KE KI</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Common combos</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Scoring K Words</h2>

<div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
  <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
    <thead class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <tr>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Word</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Points</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Length</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Notes</th>
      </tr>
