<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Essential Short K Words</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
